WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:10.000
Here’s ClientFlow, a client delivery workspace I built for service businesses. Instead of chasing updates across email, folders, and spreadsheets, both sides share one clear view.

00:10.000 --> 00:22.000
On the owner dashboard, I can see active work, open requests, and outstanding invoices. I’ll mark visual design approval complete.

00:22.000 --> 00:27.000
Progress updates immediately, and the action is recorded.

00:27.000 --> 00:42.000
